room_title: Escape room "Dark Seas Hideout" by Secret Spot Escape Rooms in San Diego
room_description: Dark Seas Hideout is an immersive pirate-themed adventure and each original, custom-made puzzle, as well as the professional set design, stays true to the Dark Seas theme.  If you are ready to have some fun and up for an exciting challenge, your crew is guaranteed to have a blast!
